---
// src/components/index/Features.astro — Why Churchify
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-secondary/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
        <img src="/john-s-lane-church-inside-st-augustine-st-catholic-popularly-known-as-dublin-ireland-35101065.webp" alt="Inside a beautiful Irish church" class="w-full h-auto" />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-3 font-semibold">Why Churchify</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">Not a Generic Website Builder</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">Churchify is purpose-built for Catholic parishes. We understand Mass times, sacrament pages, parish bulletins, and liturgical seasons — because that's all we do.</p>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold mb-1">Built Specifically for Parishes</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Mass times, sacraments, notices, bulletins — not generic blog templates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold mb-1">Daily Living Content</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Readings, feasts, saints, rosary — updated automatically every day.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold mb-1">Fully Managed Service</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Hosting, security, updates, backups — zero technical stress.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-foreground" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold mb-1">Affordable & Predictable</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">€2,000 setup, €500/year. No surprises, no hidden fees.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
